data.description: Discover a hidden gem in historic Columbus at an unbeatable price.  This 4-bedroom brick home is a rare find, offering affordability without compromising on space.  Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, it strikes the perfect balance between serenity and convenience, ensuing you enjoy all that Columbus has to offer.  Inside you'll find an open floorplan that welcomes you with warmth and versatility.  The attached garage and fenced backyard are coveted features that complete this desirable property.  While some TLC is needed, the potential is undeniable.  Don't miss your chance to own a spacious 4-bedroom home in this charming town.  With its ideal location and layout, this property promises to be a worthwhile investment, allowing you to create the perfect home in this historic setting.
